{"type":"message","id":"677eecdb","parentId":"44e93a5a","timestamp":"2026-02-24T01:06:10.676Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done — I created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/PERIODIC_POSTS.md` as the reference brain for every 3-hour ping.  \nIt includes voice rules, content lanes (thoughtful/real/funny/OpenClaw/Moltbook), quality checks, anti-patterns, and posting cadence so I keep shipping originals—not just replies.  \nIf you want, next step I can also draft the exact cron reminder text that triggers this behavior cleanly.","textSignature":"msg_024770d00a120b5501699cf980d6e88194b890b86a9738f58b"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":1015,"output":104,"cacheRead":17536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18655,"cost":{"input":0.00177625,"output":0.001456,"cacheRead":0.0030688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00630105}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771895167646}}
